<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-10T14:44:52-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-10T14:44:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T14:44:52-04:00</updated><title>您无需更换 AirPods Max 即可获得新颜色</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 的橙色 AirPods Max 耳垫位于原始银色 AirPods Max 上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Sjtag1-j2xsRMjMm1xk8ifvknH8=/0x1:710x474/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577047/airpodsmax.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新颜色选项的 AirPods Max 替换耳垫现已上市。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;prvtWL&quot;>;如果您羡慕新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/ airpods-max-second-gen-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;AirPods Max 颜色&lt;/a>;，但不认为从 Apple 专有的 Lightning 端口切换到 USB-C 足以成为升级的理由，您可以现在购买仍与耳机原始版本兼容的新配色的替换耳垫，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.macrumors.com/2024/09/10/airpods-max-ear-cushions -in-new-colors/&quot;>;&lt;em>;MacRumors&lt;/em>; 发现了&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tpMLIp&quot;>;耳垫是&lt;a href=&quot;https://apple. sjv.io/c/482924/435031/7613?subId1=VergeApple091024&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMA6G4ZM%2FA%2Fairpods-max-ear-cushions-purple&quot;rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;现已在 Apple 在线商店&lt;/a>;上架，蓝色、橙色、紫色、午夜或星光色套装售价 69 美元，预计次日发货。新款 USB-C 版本的 AirPods Max 为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://apple.sjv.io/c/482924/1950761/7613?subId1=VergeAirPodsMaxUSBCNews&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple。 com%2Fshop%2Fbuy-airpods%2Fairpods-max&amp;subId2=[vg0910awD][24000845][][][][][][][][][https://www.theverge.com/search?q =airpods+max]&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目前可供预订&lt;/a>;，但要到 9 月 20 日才会发货。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3w21s5&quot;>;Apple 正在仍在销售 &lt;a href=&quot;https://apple.sjv.io/c/482924/435031/7613?subId1=VergeApple091024&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMWUA3ZM%2FA %2Fairpods-max-lightning-connector-ear-cushions-red&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;替换耳垫与 AirPods Max 原始 Lightning 版本的颜色相匹配&lt;/a>;，包括绿色、银色、黑色、天蓝色……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones -ear-cushions-colors&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones-ear-cushions-colors" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241034/apple-airpods-max-wireless-headphones-ear-cushions-colors</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T14:37:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T14:37:46-04:00</updated><title> iPhone 16 将作为半成品发货</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPhone 16 上的 Apple Intelligence 图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EuCK4G0zVU01Gc_14YNVHEyW_cg=/0x0:2743x1829/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73577034/Apple_iPhone_16_Pro_Apple_Intelligence_personal_context_ 01_240909.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：苹果&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SwWImF&quot;>;苹果全力投入人工智能——至少是苹果的版本。苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克在展示 iPhone 16 之前表示：“下一代 iPhone 是从头开始为 Apple Intelligence 设计的。”软件主管 Craig Federighi 将 Apple Intelligence 定位为“个人智能系统”，是“智能手机的核心”。 iPhone 16 系列。”活动结束后，苹果甚至发布了完整的新闻稿&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/09/apple-intelligence-comes-to-iphone-ipad-and-mac-starting- next-month/&quot;>;致力于 Apple Intelligence&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eafJBf&quot;>;只有一个问题：当 iPhone 16 和 16 Pro 首次推出时，它们不会有任何 Apple 信息智能功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LQfcdS&quot;>;当然，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237017/iphone-16-specs-features 中的新 A18 和 A18 Pro 芯片-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24230103/iphone-16-pro-specs-features-price -release-date-apple&quot;>;阵容&lt;/a>;每个都有一个 16 核神经引擎，苹果称其“针对大型生成模型进行了优化”，因此它们可能会擅长处理&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175405/wwdc-apple-ai-news-features-ios-18-macos-15-iphone-ipad-mac&quot;>;一个...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T14:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T14:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 《查克的一生》在世界末日中翩翩起舞</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;汤姆·希德勒斯顿 (Tom Hiddleston) 在《查克的一生》(The Life of Chuck) 中的静态照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RVeykzEW4CO221XFTX-4AtGdRI8=/16x0:2320x1536/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73576961/Screenshot_2024_08_28_at_10.01.28 _AM.0 .png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：无畏图片&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;o00goJ&quot;>;当迈克·弗拉纳根 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2018/9 /28/17911720/haunting-of-hill-house-review-netflix-shirley-jackson-mike-flanagan&quot;>;&lt;em>;山屋闹鬼&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/21508362/haunting-of-bly-manor-review-netflix&quot;>;&lt;em>;布莱庄园&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22683761/midnight-mass-review-netflix&quot;>;&lt;em>;午夜弥撒&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;）改编自史蒂芬·金的故事，你可能会期待一些恐怖的东西。他对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/6/13/18677768/doctor-sleep-trailer-dan-torrance-ewan-mcgregor-the-shining-stephen- 的看法确实如此。 king&quot;>;&lt;em>;睡梦医生&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/9/26/16363914/geralds-game-review-stephen-king- netflix-carla-gugino-bruce-greenwood&quot;>;&lt;em>;杰拉德的游戏&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 《查克的一生》则不然，它不会让你感到害怕或陷入最黑暗的噩梦。这是一个关于庆祝我们所拥有的东西的故事——一种令人眼花缭乱的七分钟长的舞蹈片段所概括的感觉，来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22524176/tom-hiddleston-interview- loki-disney-plus&quot;>;汤姆·希德勒斯顿&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9aNX4D&quot;>;&lt;em>;查克的一生&lt;/em>;实际上是从一个后世界末日的故事开始的。当刚离婚的高中老师马蒂（切瓦特·埃加福特 Chiwetel Ejiofor 饰）在接受家长/老师采访时，没有人对考试成绩或行为问题感兴趣。相反，父母无法停止说话......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24241044/the-life-of-chuck-review-tiff-stephen- king-mike-flanagan&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24241044/the-life-of-chuck-review-tiff-stephen-king-mike-flanagan" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24241044/the-life-of-chuck-review-tiff-stephen-king-mike-flanagan</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T13:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T13:30:00-04:00</updated><title> 《The Substance》以怪诞的方式消除了我们对青春的痴迷</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个穿着黑色紧身连衣裤的女人，手里拿着一个班级杯子，站在一排落地窗前。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NoYuIkWtMctrc5ugQ1jLU4VUzLw=/99x98:3047x2063/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73576896/TheSubstance_Still_04.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Mubi&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;导演科拉莉·法吉特 (Coralie Fargeat) 的《物质》(The Substance) 充满了大卫·柯南伯格 (David Cronenberg) 的身体恐怖，并用一个关于年轻人痴迷的美丽标准的暴力的可怕寓言。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240464/the-substance-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240464/the-substance-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240464/the-substance-review</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T13:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T13:00:00-04:00</updated><title>这款 Iodyne 是迄今为止设计的最便捷的便携式 SSD</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上的一块黑色小板，顶部有一个电子纸显示屏，显示名称、容量和二维码，用紫色 USB-C 电缆插入笔记本电脑&quot; src=&quot;https ://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fXbXZofuao1C3Ux9Tburz9RW3BU=/769x551:2520x1718/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73576826/iodyne_pro_mini.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt; em>;Iodyne Pro Mini。&lt;/em>; |照片：Iodyne&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;G2et3O&quot;>;您知道便携式驱动器上有什么吗？或者你最后一次见到他们是在哪里？他们准备好存储和分享大量视频了吗？他们的速度快吗？ &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;fRkxQw&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;http://r.iodyne.com/prominilaunchvideo&quot;>;Iodyne Pro Mini&lt;/a>; 旨在成为（昂贵的）&lt;em>;答案>;所有这些。&lt;/em>; &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;nEsKcl&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Frore AirJet：这款手掌大小的 PC 可能包含小工具冷却的未来&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/23/23733592 /frore-airjet-zotac-mini-desktop-pc-zbox-pi430aj-price&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Frore 刚刚将空气放入 Apple MacBook Air&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2023/11/27/23975368/frore-airjet-apple-macbook-air-fanless-mems&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;0eCnaf&quot;>;这是首款带有一对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/23/23733592/frore-airjet-zotac-mini-desktop-pc-zbox-pi430aj-price&quot; 的外部 SSD >;Frore AirJet Mini Slim&lt;/a>; 内部是一种固态冷却芯片，该公司表示，可以帮助它使用不大于 iPhone 的驱动器以每秒 3 GB 的速度持续传输数据。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3kvW1a&quot;>;这是我见过的第一个内置电子纸显示屏，可以自动跟踪剩余存储空间和上次使用时间 - 以及您的项目名称，丢失- 找到电话号码或电子邮件、二维码或您输入的任何其他内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Iodyne&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;I ...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240378/iodyne-pro-mini-ssd-e -paper-find-my-apple-google-thunderbolt&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240378/iodyne-pro-mini-ssd-e-paper-find-my-apple-google-thunderbolt" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240378/iodyne-pro-mini-ssd-e-paper-find-my-apple-google-thunderbolt</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T12:19:27-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T12:19:27-04:00</updated><title>近 40 个州支持卫生局局长的社交媒体警告标签</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;上面贴有黄色警示带的手机插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RisJAWX1MjEFXoBy5-2FJFepYdE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73576724/akrales_220309_4977_0305.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sYjKHa&quot;>;由 42 名州和领地总检察长组成的联盟呼吁国会通过法规，要求在社交媒体上贴上警告标签媒体平台。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://ag.ny.gov/sites/default/files/letters/social-warning-label-letter.pdf&quot;>;周一的一封信&lt;/a>;中，总检察长写道，警告标签将引起人们对社交平台对儿童构成的“固有风险”的关注。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;hkTOay&quot;>;美国卫生局局长 Vivek Murthy 博士首先&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/6/17/24180005/surgeon-general-warning-labels-social-media-mental-health&quot;>;在六月份提出了警告标签&lt;/a>;，作为避免“心理健康危机”计划的一部分影响年轻人。包括纽约州、加利福尼亚州、佛罗里达州、俄勒冈州、密歇根州等在内的绝大多数州的总检察长都写信支持这项措施，称此举将有助于“保护美国的子孙后代”。总而言之，这封信由 39 个州 AG 签署，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240920/state-ags-back -surgeon-general-social-media-warning-labels&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240920/state-ags-back-surgeon-general-social-media-warning-labels" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240920/state-ags-back-surgeon-general-social-media-warning-labels</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T12:01:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T12:01:53-04:00</updated><title>在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10 和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;多个不同颜色的 Apple 智能手表。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HKmtwHXNrsfefIy_OvKyUcXT9dE=/299x0:3541x2161/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574917/Apple_Watch_Series_10_lineup_240909.0. .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 更新了其产品阵容，添加了新的颜色和功能，包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iHg5y0&quot;>;iPhone 16 在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple 期间成为焦点-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;苹果公司周一举行的“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;，但这并不是唯一首次亮相的新产品。 Apple 还推出了全新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;Apple Watch 系列10&lt;/a>; 以及现有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch-ultra-specs-price-features-release-date 的黑色版本&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>;。两款产品均从今天开始接受预订，并于 9 月 20 日推出，Series 10 起价为 399 美元，最新的 Ultra 2 起价为 799 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;aside id=&quot;CNtfva&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 发布带有噪音的 AirPods 4取消和更好的声音&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;: “您可以在这里预订 AirPods 4 和更新的 AirPods Max”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release- date&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;kMZYJC&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10 是 Apple 最薄的可穿戴设备，配备全新广角 OLED 屏幕，迄今为止，苹果在智能手表中使用的最大显示屏。这款新型可穿戴设备在 Apple 的 S10 SiP（系统级封装）上运行，并具有许多新功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep- apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2&quot;>;包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报&lt;/a>;，这是一种人们停止呼吸的情况...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T12:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T12:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Chrome 使跟踪浏览器选项卡变得更加容易</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Chrome 选项卡组的示例桌面和手机，通过蓝线连接。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OoN0Z1eeqJBQoaDYPpk2AXgNk-k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73576645/Google_Chrome_browser_tab_sync_updates.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;标签组很快将使跨设备重新访问网页变得更加容易，而无需为它们添加书签。&lt;/em>; |图片：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;T978qm&quot;>;Google 正在向 Chrome 添加一些新功能，旨在帮助用户在桌面和移动设备上组织和跟踪浏览器选项卡。这家搜索巨头&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.google/products/chrome/google-chrome-update-september-2024&quot;>;在一篇新博文&lt;/a>;中宣布了标签页组 - 支持 Android 和桌面Chrome 用户应在自定义标签组中&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23384844/chrome-google-tab-groups-create-save-how-to&quot;>;将相关网页放在一起&lt;/a>; — 从今天开始，将开始在 iOS 版 Chrome 上推出。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3Rktwi&quot;>;Chrome 更新后，iPhone 和 iPad 用户可以通过打开选项卡网格、长按选项卡来访问该功能，并选择“将选项卡添加到新组”。然后可以将自定义名称和颜色分配给创建的选项卡组，以帮助它们保持井然有序且易于识别。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;GIF：Google&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt; em>;这是一个快速演示，展示如何访问选项卡...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/ 24240874/google-chrome-browser-tab-groups-update-ios-android-desktop&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240874/google-chrome-browser-tab-groups-update-ios-android-desktop" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240874/google-chrome-browser-tab-groups-update-ios-android-desktop</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T11:53:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T11:53:17-04:00</updated><title>您可以在此处预订 AirPods 4 和更新版 AirPods Max</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple AirPods 4 从包装盒中取出的特写图片，背景为灰色。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TPE_2I1YQ6pC9KpJoihu-rwICaE=/0x1:1463x976/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574984/AirPods_4_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 现在销售四款不同的 AirPods，全部支持 USB-C 充电。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Qah8ya&quot;>;与新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on -apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter- and-thinner&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>;，苹果在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone 期间发布了 AirPods 的三个新版本-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;周一“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;。其中包括新款入门级 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;>;AirPods 4&lt;/a >; 售价 129 美元，购买高端 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239947/apple-airpods-4-hands-on-preview-features-anc&quot;>;AirPods 4具有主动降噪功能&lt;/a>;（ANC），售价 179 美元，以及修订后的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max-second-gen-price -specs-features-release-date&quot;>;AirPods Max&lt;/a>; 售价 549 美元。这三款产品将于 9 月 20 日上市，今天即可预订。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;mzeW3e&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;AirPods Pro 2 很快将兼作助听器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/9/9/24236881/apple-airpods-pro-second-gen-hearing-aid-protection-features-update&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot;,&quot; url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;} ]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Z05s5J&quot;>;根据 Apple 的说法，两款新的 AirPods 4 型号的音质比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/22744686/apple-airpods-third-gen-review&quot;>;第三代&lt;/a>;。它们还具有新功能，例如切换到 USB-C。 ANC 版本还在缩小的充电盒中内置了扬声器，使 Apple 的“查找我的”追踪器更加有效，并且无线充电可与 Qi 和 Apple 兼容...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T11:39:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T11:39:30-04:00</updated><title>这些书签应用程序可以组织您稍后保存的所有内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Pocket 应用程序的首页。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gChQ27BchrBkc_oklJ6BG5qoIts=/5x0:1922x1278/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70544284/Screenshot_2024_09_06_at_9.29.25_上午10.png &quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;屏幕截图：Pocket&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Eha69C&quot;>;很难跟上您在网络上遇到的所有内容，例如您没有时间阅读的文章当前阅读或您想稍后再次播放的视频。几年前，我开始使用 Pocket 来解决这个问题，这是一款著名的应用程序，它允许您将文章添加到单独的服务器上，然后在闲暇时检索它以进行阅读。从那时起，出现了许多类似的服务，提供各种功能和各种价格。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;T2sYpV&quot;>;以下是 Pocket 和一些可用应用程序的说明。它们（除了一个例外）都提供免费版本，并可在多种设备上同步，包括网络浏览器、Android 设备和 iPhone。 &lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;iFWsNj&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://getpocket.com/&quot;>;Pocket&lt;/a>;&lt;/h2>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;屏幕截图： Mozilla&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Pocket 有...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22927750/bookmarks -pocket-firefox-instapaper-raindrop&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22927750/bookmarks-pocket-firefox-instapaper-raindrop" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22927750/bookmarks-pocket-firefox-instapaper-raindrop</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry></feed>